{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Come morning time, and came, you know, the [NON-ENGLISH], which means the chief of the block, which usually, she was also a prisoner-- usually, always.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- but she had already staying in the camp for a few months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she had more experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were appointed by the Germans to be-- to be, you know, in charge of the blocks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, this [NON-ENGLISH], the woman [NON-ENGLISH], they were very good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it happened, you know, that in the men-- in the men camp, we heard, afterwards, the kapos and [NON-ENGLISH] were horrible.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were prisoner like them, but they were like savages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, the Germans came only in the morning to count us-- and in the evening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So during the day, if they had wanted to be more human to their fellow prisoner, they could have done with-- nobody will ever witness it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were all like savages, you know, because they were already so many months ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And life, it was so bad there that you cannot reason anymore what you were doing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were not any-- you can't differentiate good to evil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they were witnessing bad things about, you know, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were maybe learning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And beside that, at the-- from the very moment we arrive, till at the end, the-- the food that they give us, the little food that they give us-- like bread and-- and soup-- you know, that they're giving us, they was full of bromo, which was a substance to-- to make you, you know, like imbecile.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were not-- because in normal times, when you know you know something happening to-- to you, you rebel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there, you know, nobody rebel.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
